article.story: HOUSTON -- — DJ Richards scored 16 points, Christian Shumate had a double-double and McNeese thumped Houston Christian 105-54 on Monday night. Richards also had four steals for the Cowboys (22-3, 11-1 Southland Conference). Shumate totaled 13 points on 6-for-7 shooting and grabbed 10 rebounds. Antavion Collum made 3 of 4 shots from 3-point range and scored 13. Marcus Greene and Dominic Capriotti both scored 15 to lead the Huskies (6-17, 4-8). ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
